page_title: 'Quickstart: Use Azure OpenAI Service with the JavaScript SDK'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first chat completions call with the JavaScript SDK.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free- LTS versions of Node.js- An Azure OpenAI Service resource with either a `gpt-35-turbo` or `gpt-4` series models deployed. For more information about model deployment, see the resource deployment guide.> [!div class="nextstepaction"]> I ran into an issue with the prerequisites.
